of the areas where levers could be

19
00:01:00.477 --> 00:01:05.721
pulled on making the workplace more
accessible throughout technology.

20
00:01:05.721 --> 00:01:10.218
So, government comes into it,
advocacy groups, employers have

21
00:01:10.218 --> 00:01:15.682
responsibilities here, technology
companies for the tooling that we put out,

22
00:01:15.682 --> 00:01:19.778
education and research, so
schools that have to teach it and

23
