24
00:01:24.308 --> 00:01:26.109
So it's just kind of interesting,

25
00:01:26.109 --> 00:01:28.641
we're not on our own here
in thinking about this.

26
00:01:28.641 --> 00:01:33.416
There's groups that care a lot
about accessible workplaces

27
00:01:33.416 --> 00:01:38.108
