00:05:33.995 --> 00:05:38.976
Twitter or the accessibility world and the
disability world or disability Twitter.

94
00:05:38.976 --> 00:05:41.111
Those are not the same.

95
00:05:41.111 --> 00:05:44.940
And being a young,
eager accessibility person,

96
00:05:44.940 --> 00:05:49.311
that was kind of the first
realization I had of that a lot of

